strings.Value: "Jhod Kavken is too hard on himself. He has a kind soul, and I thank providence for our meeting."
"He has a very pretty smile! It's a shame we see it so rarely."
"It was lucky we met him. Suspicious, too... But he couldn't deceive a baby with that face. He's absolutely harmless, and hence â€” entirely useless."
"His head looks like a potato. A potatohead! Ha, ha."
